{"tid":1683710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動置頂] 11.2  「求援國際 堅守自治 」- 全球行動資訊","createTime":"2019-10-30T17:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T17:56:36.000Z","uid":126675,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff236c9cefce89cd3bba6f151a6d1de584bf618","tid":1683710,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5Rr11b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5Rr11b.jpg&h=b6fbfae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標100萬人！11.2  「求援國際 堅守自治 」流水式維園集會！英美加澳日 全球同步聲援！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671328</a> <br />\n<br />\n【112維園見】全球33個城市響應號召，一句講曬，香港人出唔出先？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqOxcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqOxcS</a><br />\n <br />\n今個星期進入運動既week 22<br />\n我哋冇0乜人手冇資源可以成日上連登update <br />\n大家可以follow twitter &amp; fb 獲得最近update<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/GlobalSolidarityHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FGlobalSolidarityHK&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=2ea6e18c\" target=\"_blank\">fb.com/GlobalSolidarityHK</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/GlobalSolidHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalSolidHK&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=9e7f2e24\" target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/GlobalSolidHK</a><br />\n <br />\n【第22星期：堅守自治 聲援香港 ✊ 不斷更新！】<br />\n<br />\n香港人反抗暴政踏入第六個月，身處海外嘅香港人一直都自發用盡方法去支援香港嘅抗爭。由6月以嚟第22個星期亦唔例外，我哋會喺各自嘅崗位上繼續努力，令民主運動真正遍地開花，全球團結對抗暴政，爭取自由自治自決。<br />\n<br />\nThis week marks the 22nd week since the fight against totalitarianism in Hong Kong erupted. Since then, overseas Hong Kongers have been supporting this fight in many different ways. This weekend, democracy loving people around the world will continue to stand with the people of Hong Kong. Here are the week 22 global solidarity events.<br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n1) 澳洲阿德萊德 -  集會 🇦🇺<br />\n<br />\n日期: 11月3號 星期日<br />\n時間: 下午2點半<br />\n地點: Rundle Mall<br />\n<br />\nAdelaide, Australia - Rally 🇦🇺<br />\n<br />\nDate: Sunday, November 3<br />\nTime: 2:30 PM<br />\nLocation: Rundle Mall<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2421379454804467/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2421379454804467%2F&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=78d87b97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2421379454804467/</a><br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n2) 澳洲布里斯本 - 集會 🇦🇺<br />\n<br />\n日期: 11月2號 星期六<br />\n時間: 下午2點<br />\n地點: Queensland Parliament House<br />\n<br />\nBrisbane, Australia - Rally 🇦🇺<br />\n<br />\nDate: Saturday, November 2<br />\nTime: 3:00 PM<br />\nLocation: Queensland Parliament House<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2346225659025229/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2346225659025229%2F&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=868b4bd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2346225659025229/</a><br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n3) 澳洲悉尼 - 遊行 🇦🇺<br />\n<br />\n日期: 11月2號 星期六<br />\n時間: 下午1點半<br />\n地點: State Library of New South Wales<br />\n<br />\nSydney, Australia - March 🇦🇺<br />\n<br />\nDate: Saturday, November 2<br />\nTime: 1:30 PM<br />\nLocation: State Library of New South Wales<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1433828236777026/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F1433828236777026%2F&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=eca4e29d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1433828236777026/</a><br />\n<br />\n=============<br />\n<br />\n4) 澳洲墨爾本 - 展覽 🇦🇺<br />\n<br />\n日期: 11月2號 星期六<br />\n時間: 中午12點<br />\n地點